<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>&quot;We move up to the final room start killing the stationary guards and roaming guards. After we've killed a lot of the roamers and the nearby stationary guards, TWC clicks up into the final hallway, and quickly moves down the hallway while we're killing some of the mobs we just pulled. They kill few of the guards inside his room and sits their entire raid inside the Lord Seru room into the spot we were preparing to set up.&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
